1.00.name: wordpress/dirtysuds-embed-pdf
1.00.description:
Will embed a PDF file using Google Docs Viewer Simply include the URL for a PDF document on it's own line, or wrapped in the embed tag like [embed]http://example.com/file.pdf[/embed] and the plugin will embed the PDF into the page using the Google Docs Viewer embed code. The url must end with .pdf

Supported attributes in the embed tag are class id title height and width
